  "title": {
   "en": "The Demon King Wants to be Friends with Me"
  },
  "altTitles": [
   {
    "zh": "魔王想跟我交朋友"
   }
  ],
  "description": {
   "en": "THE MALE LEAD SUPPORTED AND BELIEVED IN SCIENCE EVER SINCE HE WAS YOUNG AND HAD A NATURALLY UNSOCIABLE DISPOSITION. HOWEVER, SINCE HE WAS BORN IN A FAMILY WHOSE MATERNAL LINEAGE WERE SORCERERS, HE WAS CAST OUT OF THE CLAN DUE TO HIS LACK OF MAGICAL POWERS. HE AND HIS YOUNGER SISTER DEPENDED ON EACH OTHER THEREAFTER. ONE DAY, THE MALE LEAD NOTICED THAT HIS SISTER HAD GONE MISSING AND HEARD RUMOURS ABOUT THE DEMON KING’S EVIL DOINGS. BELIEVING THAT THE DEMON KING HAD ABDUCTED HIS SISTER, HE DECIDED TO CROSSDRESS TO INFILTRATE THE DEMON KING’S CITY TO SAVE HIS SISTER. UNEXPECTEDLY, THE DEMON KING IS ACTUALLY A HANDSOME GUY WHO LIKES MAKING DRESSES?!\n",
   "zh": "从小就拥戴科学、相信科学、生性孤僻的男主，却生在一个母系家族是魔法使的家庭里，因为没有魔力被逐出家族，之后和妹妹相依为命。\n某天，男主发现妹妹失踪了，听闻魔王种种劣迹，男主认定是魔王抓走了妹妹，为了妹妹决定女装混进魔王城。\n没想到，魔王居然是喜欢做小裙子的帅哥？！"
  },
